            , being in all five in number: these haveing a Writ against a person living near Turn-stile in <placeName id="t16751208-1-crimeloc2">Holbourn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t16751208-1-crimeloc2" type="placeName" value="Holbourn"></interp>
